<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="109" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="109">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="109">
<bibRefCitation author="Peters, W" journalOrPublisher="Monatsberichte der Koeniglichen Preussischen Akademie der Wissenschaften zu Berlin, Jahrgang" pageId="0" pageNumber="109" pagination="426 - 427" refId="B136" refString="Peters, W, 1861a. Eine neue Untergattung von Skorpionen. Monatsberichte der Koeniglichen Preussischen Akademie der Wissenschaften zu Berlin, Jahrgang 1861: 426 - 427" title="Eine neue Untergattung von Skorpionen." volume="1861" year="1861 a">Peters (1861a)</bibRefCitation>
described the genus 
<taxonomicName class="Arachnida" family="Hemiscorpiidae" genus="Hemiscorpius" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hemiscorpius" order="Scorpiones" pageId="0" pageNumber="109" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="109">Hemiscorpius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The first time the nominal species is cited in the text, it is incorrectly spelled as 
<taxonomicName authority="Peters, 1861" authorityName="Peters" authorityYear="1861" class="Arachnida" family="Hemiscorpiidae" genus="Hemiscorpion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hemiscorpion lepturus" order="Scorpiones" pageId="0" pageNumber="109" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lepturus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="109">Hemiscorpion lepturus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but we follow the modified spelling. Four syntypes (ZMB/Arach-43, two males, two females) are lodged in the ZMB collections.
</paragraph>
